TITLE: Configuring and Installing Python SDK from Source
DESCRIPTION: Sets the PYTHONPATH environment variable to include the SDK directories, changes to the Python SDK directory, installs required dependencies from `requirements.txt`, and installs the SDK locally using `setup.py`. This completes the setup for installing the Python SDK from source (Option 2).
